attributes.title: DONT DOWNLOAD APP!!!
attributes.review: This is the absolute worst app ever!!! It took weeks to download, and kept telling me to vote for trump the whole time!! When it finally downloaded, it kept glitching me out of the app. Finally after the 2000 try, it glitched me out of my phone, and wouldn’t let me get into it. I used my combination, and thumb print, but it kept saying it was wrong!! Then on the 200000000 try, it started singing the national anthem, (Donald trump’s version of course) and then made my fruits and veggies become alive!! I raced out of my house, but the tomatoes had some good legs. Then it started playing the song again, but louder!! “MY HAND IS HEREEEE! BAH BAHHH BAH DAAA YAAAA..” it Said from my phone. Then it started dialing donald trumps number, and he answered!! He said “omg what is it I’m busy.” Then the tomato screamed “COME HERE NOW AND SEND THEM TO THE ALIENS!!” “I’ll be right there.” Donald trump replied. He came in his orange helicopter, and said in alien. “Hello aliens, it is Donald trump. Will you please take this wonderful, but rather biggly human? Gosh will it fit in ur ship?” Then the aliens came and said “hello Cheeto man, we have come.” They proceeded to abduct me and took me to their ship. Then I saw that the aliens were all Donald trumps!!! There were baby Cheeto men, and Cheeto women, and there was the leader, who was the spitting image of the Cheeto man in office. They said “your app is wonderful!! We must cool you to a crisp at once!! You know Donald Cheeto Trump likes his steaks rock solid.” They then, put Cheeto dust on me, and put me in an oven. They cooked me to a crisp, and sent me down to Donald Cheeto Trump. Donald then decided to take out his fork and knife, and then said “it’s not rock solid! Out to the trash!” This was my chance to escape. I ran out of the dumpster and deleted the app. But the music still played!! And it kept going over and over “Vote for trump!” I do not recommend getting this app, it will scar you mentally and physically for life.
